267
00:13:37,863 --> 00:13:38,787
What's your name?

268
00:13:40,646 --> 00:13:42,729
Kanae... Tsuchida.

269
00:13:42,848 --> 00:13:46,214
Yeah... that was beautiful... I wanna hear it again!

270
00:13:46,239 --> 00:13:48,152
Stop teasing me, Kanie!

271
00:13:48,614 --> 00:13:53,058
No way... How could I possibly stop teasing
