285
00:14:22,771 --> 00:14:25,120
Me and this cutie are about to get busy!

286
00:14:25,145 --> 00:14:26,259
K-Kanie!

287
00:14:26,284 --> 00:14:27,337
Trust mii.

288
00:14:29,913 --> 00:14:30,900
Sorry babe...

289
00:14:30,925 --> 00:14:33,680
You're just gonna have to wait
in line for the next time... Mii!

290
00:14:33,705 --> 00:14:36,249
That's gross! How can you talk like that?!

291
00:14:36,523 --> 00:14:37,927
You'll be sorry.

292
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:41,461
I'm telling Miss Sento!

293
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:43,428
Shiina's acting weird today-mii.

294
00:14:43,513 --> 00:14:45,692
Kanie, how do you know that girl?

295
00:14:45,717 --> 00:14:47,707
She's just some chick I work with-mii.

296
00:14:47,779 --> 00:14:50,088
Anyway, I think we're alone now so why don't you...

297
00:14:50,223 --> 00:14:51,146
What now-mii?

298
00:14:51,171 --> 00:14:54,676
I don't know what to think of you saying
"mii" every 10 seconds like that, Kanie.

299
00:14:54,701 --> 00:14:58,870
Who cares-mii? Now come over here and
let me show you the meaning of pleasure-mii!

300
00:14:58,895 --> 00:15:01,253
What kind of relationship do you have with her?

301
00:15:01,278 --> 00:15:05,948
Plus, isn't Sento that quiet girl who's
been really friendly with you lately?

302
00:15:05,973 --> 00:15:08,027
Does that make me girlfriend number 3?

303
00:15:08,052 --> 00:15:11,025
Listen baby, the whole thing's
pretty complicated, alright?

304
00:15:11,050 --> 00:15:13,456
